content: ITW Consumer Group: Holds the market leading brands for both trade and retail. These brands offer your business and consumers unsurpassed confidence in the selection of hardware and fastener products. ITW Consumer Group: Integrates category management principles into all levels of our retail operations. Whatever the project, category management CATEGORY MANAGMENT focuses on increased efficiency & profits for your store. ITW Consumer Group: Representatives and Account Management have detailed insight into the market and are able to provide your business with solutions that are immediate to your needs. Our extensive experience is a testament of our professional standards at all times. ITW Consumer Group: Provides a specialist training platform that’s focused on delivering your team a comprehensive & informative program that will set your business apart from your competition. ITW Consumer Group: Provides fully self sufficient distribution centres based in the three locations - Melbourne, Brisbane & Perth. Thus complemented by a group of dedicated Sales & Marketing professionals commited to improving your business. ITW Consumer Group: Is focused on innovation in order to discover new ways of creating value to your business. The Bright Spark innovation initiative ensures that our business continues to evolve and improve so that we continue to offer you the best in products and services.

of creating value to your business. The Bright Spark innovation initiative ensures that our business continues to evolve and improve so that we continue to offer you the best in products and services. ITW Consumer Group: Provides your business & ultimately your customers with total category solutions, offering a “one stop” location for key ranges. Therefore driving profits & enhancing the shopping experience. ITW Consumer Group: Actively invests in merchandising systems that create an “Easy to Shop” environment. These systems are designed to reinforce service, quality & confidence within your customers.
